WEBVTT

00:05.341 --> 00:06.508
(pilot screams)

00:10.163 --> 00:12.180
(exclaiming)

00:16.452 --> 00:18.403
(school bell ringing)

00:21.007 --> 00:22.090
(Barney belches)

00:22.124 --> 00:24.092
(whistle blows)

00:24.126 --> 00:26.127
(yells)

00:28.000 --> 00:34.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:42.957 --> 00:44.391
(tires screech)

00:45.760 --> 00:47.160
D'oh!

00:47.195 --> 00:48.161
(tires screeching)

00:48.196 --> 00:49.796
(grunts)

00:53.201 --> 00:55.202
(Bart chuckles)

00:58.706 --> 00:59.965
(grunts, groans)

00:59.990 --> 01:03.990
<font color="#00FF00">♪ The Simpsons 25x01 ♪</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">Homerland</font>
Original Air Date on September 29, 2013

01:03.991 --> 01:07.491
